Subject: Re: Weather > Dashboard for Brazil > port = NOT updated 
 
The issue here lies with the access of INMET data via their homepage. For the last few weeks, we have been having issues downloading their weather station data and accessing their homepage in general. For example, this morning I cannot load even the starting page of their homepage.

Apparently, this is not an issue when accessing INMET from Brazil, according to Lucas. I will speak with Benoit about trying out a VPN endpoint in Brazil to see if this can resolve this persistent download issue.
